10:53.150 --> 10:54.080
Gundik Ling,

10:54.240 --> 10:55.370
Tuan Fei dah datang.

10:57.670 --> 10:59.470
Cepatlah jemput Tuan Fei masuk.

11:09.030 --> 11:09.690
Gundik Ling

11:10.000 --> 11:11.000
