12:26.480 --> 12:28.740
Jika apa-apa terjadi kepada baginda...

13:12.960 --> 13:14.600
Apa dah berlaku?

13:14.670 --> 13:15.670
Apa dah berlaku?

13:15.960 --> 13:17.360
Tunggulah sekejap lagi.

13:17.480 --> 13:18.870
Kanda.

13:18.870 --> 13:20.000
Kanda berada di sini.

13:20.000 --> 13:20.480
Kanda.

13:20.480 --> 13:21.240
Tuanku!

13:22.000 --> 13:23.200
Kanda berada di sini!

13:23.670 --> 13:27.030
- Tuanku.
- Tuanku!

13:27.200 --> 13:28.150
Liu Chu.

13:28.790 --> 13:29.600
Liu Chu.

13:30.030 --> 13:30.840
Liu Chu.

13:34.840 --> 13:35.900
- Tuanku.
- Tuanku.

13:39.790 --> 13:40.630
Ini...

13:43.670 --> 13:45.270
Tak mungkin.

13:46.030 --> 13:47.000
Baginda...

13:48.150 --> 13:49.550
Baginda...

13:51.870 --> 13:53.030
Dah mangkat.

13:54.750 --> 13:55.870
Tuanku!

13:56.150 --> 13:59.630
Tuanku!

13:59.630 --> 14:01.320
Tak mungkin.

14:01.320 --> 14:03.360
Tuanku.

14:03.360 --> 14:04.480
Tuanku.

14:04.600 --> 14:06.730
Kenapa tuanku mangkat begitu sahaja?

14:12.320 --> 14:13.360
Apa dah berlaku?

14:15.600 --> 14:16.440
Sudahlah!

14:17.750 --> 14:18.550
Pengawal!

14:18.840 --> 14:20.440
Tahan Han Yunling dan Xiao Chi,

14:20.440 --> 14:21.670
